text: __NOTOC__ Year 294 (CCXCIV) was a common year starting on Monday of the Julian calendar. == Events == === By place === ==== Roman Empire ==== * Galerius, Roman Caesar in the Balkan, fights the Goths, Marcomanni, Sarmatians, and Carpi. * Emperor Diocletian goes with the young Constantine I the Great to Egypt. He besieges Alexandria. They take down "emperor" Achilleus. ==== Asia ==== * Tuoba Luguan succeeds his nepnew Tuoba Fu as chieftain of the Tuoba clan. == Births == * Sima Bao, prince of the Jin Dynasty (d. 320) == Deaths == * Tuoba Fu, chieftain of the Chinese Tuoba clan Category:290s
